      "message": "tast_vm is essentially a hardware feature because presence of the feature is determined at run time. It was introduced as a pseudo software dependency because we didn\u0027t have hardware dependency support at that time.\n\nConsidering that, using tast_vm to decide presence of /etc/os-release sounds weird; content of /etc should be fully determined at build time, so we should be able to construct the condition from pure software features only.\n\nDo you know why /etc/os-release is present on some boards while not on other boards, and what is exact difference?",
