      "message": "My suspicion is that it is related to being a Chromium vs Chrome image. We first attempted to fix the issue of the missing /etc/os-release file with crrev.com/c/2893002 but had to be reverted since it broke other tast tests: crrev.com/c/2892356\n\nConceptually fwupd is not to different from flashrom as it is used to flash firmware and it does not make much sense in a VM either way. I could just simply update the comment if that makes more sense. Even though I would like to have that warning there for the future in case someone thinks that it makes sense on a VM.",
